Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.75,Default-3,,0,0,33,,过去与现在都已凋零\N{\rEng}"The past and present wilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.66,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我充盈它们 又将它们掏空\N{\rEng}"I have filled them, emptied them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.53,Default-3,,0,0,33,,然后继续去充盈未来的下一折页\N{\rEng}"and proceed to fill my next fold of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:10.75,Default-3,,0,0,33,,云端的倾听者啊！有何秘密要向我倾诉？\N{\rEng}"Listener up there! What have you to confide to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.67,Default-3,,0,0,33,,当我细嗅暮色时 直视我的面庞\N{\rEng}"Look in my face while I snuff the sidle of evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:18.76,Default-3,,0,0,33,,放心说吧 无人能闻得见 我只多留片刻\N{\rEng}"Talk honestly, no one else hears you, and I stay only a minute longer."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:21.24,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我是否自相矛盾？\N{\rEng}"Do I contradict myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.77,Default-3,,0,0,33,,好吧 那我就自相矛盾\N{\rEng}"Very well then, I contradict myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.60,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我心疆无限 我包罗万象\N{\rEng}I am large, I contain multitudes."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.77,Default-3,,0,0,33,,天哪\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.25,Default-3,,0,0,33,,怎么了？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:33.89,Default-3,,0,0,33,,什么事让你打断惠特曼的诗？\N{\rEng}Clearly something more interesting than Whitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:36.59,Default-3,,0,0,33,,是加州 那又地震了\N{\rEng}California. There was another earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.98,Default-3,,0,0,33,,从圣巴巴拉到弗雷斯诺一大片地都没了...\N{\rEng}A huge chunk's gone from Santa Barbara to Fresno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.55,Default-3,,0,0,33,,-太可怕了 -...沉入大海了\N{\rEng}-It's fucking crazy. -Into the ocean.
