Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.13,Note,,0,0,0,,{\move(150,170,130,170)\frz31\fs12)\1c00222222}无网络连接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:44.61,Default-3,,0,0,33,,冷静\N{\rEng}Settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.23,Default-3,,0,0,33,,没网了\N{\rEng}Got no connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.25,Default-3,,0,0,33,,你们有网吗？\N{\rEng}Anybody else have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.14,Default-3,,0,0,33,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:59.50,Default-3,,0,0,33,,抱歉 网还用不了\N{\rEng}Oh, eh, sorry. Network's still down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.87,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(144,170)\fs10\blur0.2\1c00222222}无网络连接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.92,Default-3,,0,0,33,,不过 这有纸质文件\N{\rEng}I've got his file here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.96,Default-3,,0,0,33,,迪伦最近在摸鱼\N{\rEng}Uh, Dylan's been diving lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.86,Default-3,,0,0,33,,这学期他成绩从A和B跌到了D\N{\rEng}I mean, this semester, he's gone from As and Bs to Ds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.26,Default-3,,0,0,33,,你有纸质备份？\N{\rEng}You keep hard copies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.58,Default-3,,0,0,33,,当网时好时坏时就开始保存了\N{\rEng}When the network started acting up, a lot of us started keeping hard copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.63,Default-3,,0,0,33,,你觉得这次网还能恢复吗？\N{\rEng}What do you think? I mean, you think it's coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.56,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我不知道\N{\rEng}Well, I don't, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.50,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我还记得互联网诞生前的世界\N{\rEng}I remember the world before the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.98,Default-3,,0,0,33,,没网的惨状不难想象\N{\rEng}Why is it so hard to imagine carrying on without it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.44,Default-3,,0,0,33,,对吧？\N{\rEng}It is, though, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.72,Default-3,,0,0,33,,还能恢复网吗？还有戏吗？\N{\rEng}How do we go back? How... Can we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.51,Default-3,,0,0,33,,如果这次彻底没戏了怎么活？\N{\rEng}What if it's down for good this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:27.79,Default-3,,0,0,33,,还没网\N{\rEng}Internet's still down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.23,Default-3,,0,0,33,,是没网 但别担心\N{\rEng}Yeah, but lucky for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.31,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我有所有学生的纸质文件\N{\rEng}I've got hard copies for each student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.25,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我有预感\N{\rEng}I think this might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.61,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我感觉这次网不会恢复了\N{\rEng}I don't think it's coming back this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.02,Default-3,,0,0,33,,你八成是对的\N{\rEng}You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.82,Default-3,,0,0,33,,但重点是艾米丽 她开始旷课了\N{\rEng}But I do think we should talk about Emily.  Her attendance has really fallen off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.37,Default-3,,0,0,33,,她旷课了？\N{\rEng}Her attendance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.87,Default-3,,0,0,33,,全球旷工旷课都破天荒了\N{\rEng}Absenteeism's at an all-time high all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.87,Default-3,,0,0,33,,医生旷 飞行员旷 警察也旷\N{\rEng}We got doctors and pilots and cops
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:49.14,Default-3,,0,0,33,,大家都他妈擅离职守\N{\rEng}and everyone's just pissing the fuck off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.92,Default-3,,0,0,33,,但你却只想着艾米丽？\N{\rEng}But you, you want to talk to us about Emily?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.01,Default-3,,0,0,33,,现在还怎么上课？\N{\rEng}How are they supposed to study, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.14,Default-3,,0,0,33,,网络崩溃已经八个月了\N{\rEng}Web's been on the fritz for eight months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.04,Default-3,,0,0,33,,有一半网站都是乱码\N{\rEng}Half those sites are just garbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.93,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我懂 网坏了\N{\rEng}I mean, I get it, sites go dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.78,Default-3,,0,0,33,,但其他问题呢？\N{\rEng}But what about all that other stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.42,Default-3,,0,0,33,,有些网站还好\N{\rEng}Like, sites are there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:07.58,Default-3,,0,0,33,,但都是错字和错误标点\N{\rEng}but all the punctuation's wrong. words spelled wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.03,Default-3,,0,0,33,,你能解释吗？\N{\rEng}How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.42,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我不能\N{\rEng}Well, I can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.49,Default-3,,0,0,33,,但布莱恩还能来上课\N{\rEng}but Brian can still prepare for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.56,Default-3,,0,0,33,,即便没网 课本都还在啊\N{\rEng}I mean, the library's still here. Internet or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.54,Default-3,,0,0,33,,色情网站没了\N{\rEng}Pornhub's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:24.60,Default-3,,0,0,33,,安德森老师 你知道吗？\N{\rEng}Did you know that, Mr. Anderson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.44,Default-3,,0,0,33,,呃 是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah, I, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.59,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我 我 我听说了 是的\N{\rEng}I, I, I had noticed that. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.70,Default-3,,0,0,33,,对不起 小布给你添麻烦了\N{\rEng}Sorry if Bri's been any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.86,Default-3,,0,0,33,,这家就我一人了\N{\rEng}It's just me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:37.32,Default-3,,0,0,33,,他妈妈跑了 我不知道去哪了\N{\rEng}His mom... she left, I don't know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.97,Default-3,,0,0,33,,听说最近这事常见\N{\rEng}That's been happening a lot more I hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.71,Default-3,,0,0,33,,人们只是玩失踪\N{\rEng}people just ghosting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.50,Default-3,,0,0,33,,她高中那会儿认识个无缘的男友\N{\rEng}Hers was some star-crossed boyfriend from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.10,Default-3,,0,0,33,,待在一起有一个月吧\N{\rEng}They dated a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.14,Default-3,,0,0,33,,那该死的一个月\N{\rEng}Goddamn month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:54.03,Default-3,,0,0,33,,就为了那一个月 她竟然丢下二十年的感情\N{\rEng}She's gonna throw 20 years in the trash to chase down a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.99,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我猜她一直藕断丝连他\N{\rEng}I guess she never stopped thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.86,Default-3,,0,0,33,,谁心里没有放不下的人\N{\rEng}I guess we've all got someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.41,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我懂 我懂\N{\rEng}I mean, I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:04.67,Default-3,,0,0,33,,就像那些穿紫袍说的那样 要真是末日了\N{\rEng}if it really is the end, like those kooks in the purple robes say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.91,Default-3,,0,0,33,,最终和谁一起面对呢？\N{\rEng}then who do you want to be with for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.90,Default-3,,0,0,33,,她要抛弃骨肉吗？\N{\rEng}But to leave her son?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.84,Default-3,,0,0,33,,对了 她说会回来的\N{\rEng}Uh, she says she'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.33,Default-3,,0,0,33,,我也不确定\N{\rEng}I don't know. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.86,Default-3,,0,0,33,,该死的色情网站\N{\rEng}Fuckin' Pornhub.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.76,Default-3,,0,0,33,,万一永远不回来了呢？\N{\rEng}What if that never comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.04,Default-3,,0,0,33,,真他妈的倒霉\N{\rEng}Fuckin' tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:35.11,Default-3,,0,0,33,,就算这真是一切的结局\N{\rEng}I mean, even if it is the end of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:39.14,Default-3,,0,0,33,,这也提前把我结束了\N{\rEng}that's just fuckin' mean.
